      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FUTURE REFERENCE (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fifth (30.63) in a Grade 5 at Dapto over 520m. Got the money at her only try from this box. Should be very hard to beat this time. MIRACULOUS TOMMY (6) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (17.56) behind Hear Me Roar at Richmond Straight. Expected to feature again. MAJOR TED (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by one length at Bulli in a handy 19.25 beating Freed Desire. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected again. SHE'S GAGA (2) got up for a shock win last time and is in the mix again.",
